{"tid":1854452,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［問鏡頭意見］ Fujifilm 想買 23mm 街攝","createTime":"2020-01-31T13:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T16:05:38.000Z","uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a98530559a34c495d71dfa6ca316d175cf78406","tid":1854452,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"小弟想買枝街攝鏡頭，筆直 2k-3k ，心水有2枝<br />\n<br />\n1） Fuji XF 23mm f2 全新<br />\n2)   Sigma art 24mm 1.4  EF mount 二手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）主要考慮 重量（&lt;300g)、size  隱蔽性，方便街攝，影人冇咁出眾。 <br />\n<br />\n2）抵玩，art 畫質唔係講笑，但係重到仆街 (600g)、大舊，街攝會唔會好礙眼<br />\n<br />\n光圈唔係最主要考慮，因為唔太需要散景。暫定唔考慮 XF 23mm f1.4<br />\n<br />\n小弟未比較過兩枝鏡頭既畫質，但係覺得sigma art 會佔優。<br />\n<br />\n跪求意見！"},{"pid":"79fb29c1ffb6e960e02f45abcdd66205ad57196b","tid":1854452,"uid":255414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"XF 27mm 2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725c0214bf9096dac161b55eda93053cd2a3e7cf","tid":1854452,"uid":5557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fb29c1ffb6e960e02f45abcdd66205ad57196b","tid":1854452,"uid":255414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"XF 27mm 2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39db14d0c21863e64d6e5954fe2f631f75c4b0c1","tid":1854452,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"xf 23 f2啦<br />\n又輕又快又有wr"},{"pid":"cf76f34d18e691bf559bdc5d2d090d481a893c6b","tid":1854452,"uid":5469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"你又驚23/2影人唔夠出眾<br />\n二手24art+個adepter搞咁